text: Ultra highnetworth individuals UHNWI are defined as having a net worth of at least US30 million in constant 2018 dollars. It is the wealth segment above veryhighnetworth individuals gt5 million and highnetworthindividuals gt1 million. Although they constitute only 0.003 of the worlds population less than 1 in 33 thousands, they hold 13 of the worlds total wealth.
